item.title: Anna Plaschke
item.description: My biography My name is Anna Plaschke, I am 23 years old and I grew up in the German speaking region of Italy, South Tyrol. I went to the German speaking school Realgymnasium Bozen and did an exchange in the Italian counterpart-school, Liceo Scientifico Torricelli. I graduated with honours in Business, Economics and Social Sciences from Vienna University of Economics and Business and did an exchange semester in Hongkong.
